summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 22W, Page 75 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone properties in the 4200 block of Francis Avenue North and Dayton Avenue North from Lowrise 1 (L-1) and Single Family Attached (SFA) to Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) Zone. (Petition of John Bachman; C.F. 296111).
